2715b9a4 wp-block-column-is-layout-flow\" style=\"padding-top:0;padding-right:0px;padding-bottom:0;padding-left:0px\">\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image aligncenter size-large\"><a href=\"https://www.indiebound.org/book/9781982176808\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"91\" height=\"31\" src=\"/images/legacy/2021/09/indie.svg\" alt=\"indie\" class=\"wp-image-179\"/></a></figure>\n</div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-column is-vertically-aligned-center is-layout-flow wp-container-core-column-is-layout-2715b9a4 wp-block-column-is-layout-flow\" style=\"padding-top:0;padding-right:0px;padding-bottom:0;padding-left:0px\">\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image aligncenter size-full is-resized\"><a href=\"https://www.simonandschuster.com/books/State-Change/Robin-Berzin/9781982176808\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"182\" height=\"62\" src=\"/images/legacy/2021/09/Simon-Schuster-Button.png\" alt=\"Simon-Schuster-Button\" class=\"wp-image-363\" style=\"width:95px;height:auto\"/></a></figure>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-group alignfull is-layout-flow wp-block-group-is-layout-flow\" style=\"padding-right:0;padding-left:0\">\n<div class=\"wp-block-group alignfull has-global-padding is-layout-constrained wp-container-core-group-is-layout-44f4dd63 wp-block-group-is-layout-constrained\" style=\"padding-top:0;padding-right:0;padding-bottom:0;padding-left:0\">\n<div class=\"wp-block-group has-global-padding is-layout-constrained wp-block-group-is-layout-constrained\">\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading has-text-align-left has-superbfont-large-font-size\">&#8220;Ninety-nine percent of our health happens to us outside a doctor’s office.&#8221;</h3>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-group is-vertical is-content-justification-left is-layout-flex wp-container-core-group-is-layout-2290e706 wp-block-group-is-layout-flex\">\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading has-text-align-center has-primary-color has-text-color has-superbfont-small-font-size\">Robin Berzin MD</h2>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"has-text-align-left has-primary-color has-text-color has-superbfont-small-font-size\"><em>State Change, Chapter 1</em></p>\n</div>\n</div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-group has-global-padding is-layout-constrained wp-block-group-is-layout-constrained\">\n<p>State Change: End Anxiety, Beat Burnout, And Ignite A New Baseline Of Energy And Flow is filled with science-backed, actionable guidance on how you can achieve your very own state change.&nbsp;</p>\n\n\n\n<p>But what is a #StateChange? It is a metamorphosis of your emotional and mental health triggered by a change in your physical health. All too often our mental and physical health are seen as separate—the former treated by a psychiatrist, the latter by your regular doctor. I present a different approach, one that acknowledges the intricate relationship between our bodies and our minds. One that asks us to first take care of our bodies and understand our physical triggers so that we may rejuvenate and energize our minds. This is what State Change is about. It is a holistic approach to health and wellness. It delivers a data-backed step-by-step way to rethink your health and take back control of your life.&nbsp;</p>\n\n\n\n<p>#StateChange is a book for all of us, right now. It is my way of sharing with each and every one of you that a more impassioned, empowered, energetic, and healthier life is possible. Especially when so many of us are feeling burned out, fatigued, low energy, anxious, and altogether unwell. It is time for a #StateChange.</p>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-group has-global-padding is-layout-constrained wp-container-core-group-is-layout-2217c10c wp-block-group-is-layout-constrained\" style=\"padding-top:var(--wp--preset--spacing--superbspacing-small);padding-right:var(--wp--preset--spacing--superbspacing-small);padding-bottom:var(--wp--preset--spacing--superbspacing-small);padding-left:var(--wp--preset--spacing--superbspacing-small)\">\n<hr class=\"wp-block-separator has-text-color has-primary-hover-color has-alpha-channel-opacity has-primary-hover-background-color has-background\"/>\n</div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-group alignfull has-global-padding is-layout-constrained wp-container-core-group-is-layout-3e6c37bc wp-block-group-is-layout-constrained\" style=\"margin-top:var(--wp--preset--spacing--superbspacing-small);margin-bottom:var(--wp--preset--spacing--superbspacing-small)\">\n<div class=\"wp-block-group alignfull is-layout-flow wp-container-core-group-is-layout-7828984b wp-block-group-is-layout-flow\" style=\"margin-top:0;margin-bottom:0;padding-right:0;padding-left:0\">\n<div class=\"wp-block-group alignwide has-global-padding is-content-justification-center is-layout-constrained wp-block-group-is-layout-constrained\">\n<div class=\"wp-block-columns alignwide are-vertically-aligned-center is-layout-flex wp-container-core-columns-is-layout-6376d770 wp-block-columns-is-layout-flex\" style=\"margin-top:0;margin-bottom:0;padding-right:0;padding-left:0\">\n<div class=\"wp-block-column is-vertically-aligned-center is-layout-flow wp-container-core-column-is-layout-30be4402 wp-block-column-is-layout-flow\">\n<p class=\"has-text-align-left has-custom-pixels-dark-color has-text-color has-link-color has-superbfont-large-font-size wp-elements-57c86e442d7c47c5214358bc00f0ca7c\">&#8220;Innovative, strategic, and wise, Dr. Berzin has created a gentle toolkit for reaching new levels of energy, clarity, and ease. Let her be your guide to a new baseline of well-being.&#8221;</p>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-group is-vertical is-content-justification-left is-layout-flex wp-container-core-group-is-layout-2290e706 wp-block-group-is-layout-flex\">\n<h4 class=\"wp-block-heading has-text-align-center has-custom-pixels-dark-color has-text-color\">Erica Chidi</h4>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"has-text-align-left has-custom-pixels-medium-color has-text-color has-superbfont-small-font-size\">co-founder &amp; CEO of LOOM</p>\